description: We are committed to the philosophy that food should be fun, affordable and delicious. We specialize in the flavors of Moroccan Street Food, but we’ve been known to throw in a Moroccan taco , vegetarian and even a Raw Vegan Dish.  Our menu is constantly changing. We’re slaves to our creative drive, so expect the unexpected.CREATIVE CATERING FOR UNFORGETTABLE EVENTSThe heart of our business is our catering. Let us customize a menu for you. We guarantee to make your next event the most memorable one of the year!
name: Wheelie Gourmet
